You shouldn&#39;t access an auto variable of one method from another method. There are many reasons for that: the most obvious is that this variable is always new and is not alive after you exit the function. In your case these methods doesn&#39;t call each other, so the lifetime of `z` and `x` even doesn&#39;t overlap.

